creator: Fit Cloud Technology Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Track your progress and access exercise programs with The YMCA Halo Foothills app.

Set goals and create your own workouts. Request and receive workouts from a personal trainer.

The app connects with compatible Life Fitness and Cybex cardio equipment, enabling automatic logging of your workouts.

Sign up for your favourite gym classes from the YMCA Halo Foothills app.

Features:

My Activity
View your workout history. Get an informative summary of your total workout minutes, planned and achieved exercises.

My Classes
Join the classes you want to attend in your gym, and add them to your personal calendar.

My Goal
Set a goal, and give yourself a deadline. Decide on a goal which best suits you and stay motivated to meet that goal. A timeline offers a reminder of the goal and a countdown to your deadline.

My Training
Create your own workouts - or receive a personalised training plan from a trainer at your gym, based on your fitness goals.

My Challenges
Join Challenges and compete against other members in your facility! Participate in ongoing and future challenges. Check the challenge leaderboard for live updates on your position!

My Stats
Keep a log of your body weight, height, body fat %, heart rate and blood pressure. Your coach will be able to see all recorded entries to support you in achieving your fitness goals.
descriptionShort: YMCA Halo Foothills

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: In this release we've focused on tidying up some bugs and improving performance

Within a workout, "Connect" to activate your camera and scan a QR Code. Just add the sets and the exercise will be added into your session!

We've also resolved some minor bugs!
